reviews.text: Absolutely the best bakery in Barrie! The croissants are perfectly flaky and buttery. I come here every Saturday morning.
Amazing coffee and pastries. The staff is super friendly and the atmosphere is cozy. Highly recommend the almond croissant!
Great bakery with fresh items daily. Only wish they had more seating during busy hours.
Best craft brewery in the area! Great selection of beers and the atmosphere is fantastic. Love the weekend live music.
Good beer selection, but can get crowded on weekends. The Smashbomb Atomic IPA is incredible.
Fresh sushi and excellent service. The dragon roll is my favorite. Definitely the best Japanese restaurant in Barrie.
Great sushi at reasonable prices. The lunch specials are a steal. Can get busy during dinner time.
Amazing omakase experience! The chef really knows what he's doing. Worth every penny.
Authentic Italian cuisine in a beautiful setting. The homemade pasta is to die for. Perfect for date night!
Best Italian food outside of Italy! The wine list is excellent and the tiramisu is heavenly.
